com.pcr3w.jscraft.minecraft.block

Class Block

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pcr3w.jscraft.minecraft.mod.JsRegisteredClass
      • com.pcr3w.jscraft.minecraft.mod.MinecraftClassWrapper
        • com.pcr3w.jscraft.minecraft.block.Block
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IWrapper
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Crop, Fluid

    public class Block
extends MinecraftClassWrapper
    Wraps around a Minecraft block, allowing for all of the methods and fields to be accessed from JsCraft
    Author:
    pcr3w
